data.description: Discover this delightful 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome with a beautifully upgraded, neutral-toned kitchen. The private yard showcases low-maintenance synthetic turf, offering an ideal balance of sophistication and easy maintenance. You'll have access to a variety of community amenities, including two pools, a spa, picturesque walking paths, and more. This Mesa location is incredibly convenient, with grocery stores and other essential amenities just a short walk away.
